Headhunterz, formerly known as Nasty D-Tuners, is a Dutch DJ/producer team, consisting of Willem Rebergen (born September 12, 1985) and Bobby van Putten. Their own label Scantraxx Reloaded is a sublabel of Scantraxx. Van Putten stopped temporarily with DJing and producing so that he can finish his study.

At the age of nine, Rebergen sang in a children's choir that recorded several CDs. One year later, he started voice acting and is still doing this. He gained his first major experience as a DJ at Defqon 1, a huge techno event in the Netherlands, where he was discovered by The Prophet.
